---
title: Family-Style Grilled Steak Lettuce Wraps with Pickled Veggies, Creamy Gochujang Sauce & Cold Peanut Noodles
description: These fresh lettuce wraps are filled with zesty, brown sugar-grilled steak, pickled cabbage and carrots, fresh scallions, and a creamy gochujang drizzle. Alongside,you'll enjoy chilled peanut noodles. The best part? Serve this quick and easy summer meal family-style so you can enjoy the sunshine with all your favorite people.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/family-style-grilled-steak-lettuce-wraps-0533a973.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/family-style-grilled-steak-lettuce-wraps-62965bbc32fffbd6110ee754-aeab813f.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/family-style-grilled-steak-lettuce-wraps-62965bbc32fffbd6110ee754
servings: 2
time required: 35 minutes
course: main course
author: Sara Heilman
cuisine: Asian
